                    "text": " The program was just segfaulting at strange different locations.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " It is a pain to debug when you have no idea what are you dealing with.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Having own \"stack\" for this purpose is a bit more work, but can save a lot of work later when you encounter problems.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
